Netflix Project

In [ ]:

Netflix is one of the most popular media and video streaming platforms. They have over 10000 movies or tv shows available on their platform, as of mid- 2021, they have over 222M Subscribers globally

Attribute Information¶

Show_id: Unique ID for every Movie / Tv Show
Type: Identifier - A Movie or TV Show
Title: Title of the Movie / Tv Show
Director: Director of the Movie
Cast: Actors involved in the movie/show
Country: Country where the movie/show was produced
Date_added: Date it was added on Netflix
Release_year: Actual Release year of the movie/show
Rating: TV Rating of the movie/show
Duration: Total Duration - in minutes or number of seasons
Listed_in: Genre
Description: The summary description

Objective¶

Analyze the data and generate insights that could help Netflix in deciding which type of shows/movies to produce and how they can grow the business in different countries?

Questions are Analized¶

1. How has the number of movies released per year changed over the last 20-30 years
2. Comparison of tv shows vs. movies.
3. best time to launch a TV show.
4. Analysis of actors/directors of different types of shows/movies.
5. TV Shows than movies in recent years
6. content is available in different countries

Content growth over the year.¶

In [43]:
yearly_shows=df[df.type =='TV Show']['release_year'].value_counts().sort_index(ascending=False).head(15)
yearly_movies=df[df.type =='Movie']['release_year'].value_counts().sort_index(ascending=False).head(15)

yearly_movies.plot(figsize=(12, 6), linewidth=2.5, color='maroon',label="Movies / year",ms=3)
yearly_shows.plot(figsize=(12, 6), linewidth=2.5, color='blue',label="TV Shows / year")
plt.xlabel("Years", fontsize=15)
plt.ylabel("Number", fontsize=15)
plt.legend(loc="upper left")
plt.title("Production Growth Yearly", y=1.02, fontsize=22,fontweight="bold");
  • Growth in the number of movies on Netflix is much higher than tv shows.
  • From 2015 we can see a noticeable addition in the number of movies and tv shows uploaded by Netflix on its platform.
  • The highest number of movies and tv shows got added in 2017 and 2018.
  • Over the period of time no of movies and Tv shows increases but have droped after 2019 due to covid 19.

Insights¶

  1. There are about 70% movies and 30% TV shows on Netflix.
  2. The United States has the highest number of content on Netflix by a huge margin followed by India.
  3. Rajiv Chilaka and Jan Sulter collectively have directed the most content on Netflix.
  4. Anupam Kher has acted in the highest number of films on Netflix.
  5. It is estimated that almost 64% of movies have a runtime between 80 minutes to 120 minutes.

  6. The number of movies release have significantly increased and have dropped in 2019 because of Covid 19.
  7. TV-MA tops the charts, indicating that mature content is more popular on Netflix.
  8. South Korea and Japan are the only two countries in the top 7 that produce more TV shows.
  9. Other than India, all the other top content producing countries offer the most TV-MA (Adults) rated content. The most popular and widely produced content in India is TV-14 (above 14).
  10. We have reached a conclusion from analysis from the content added over years that Netflix is focusing movies and TV shows
  11. Five most popular genres in recent years are International movies, Dramas, Comedies, International TV Shows and Documentaries.

  12. Most of these contents are released either in the month beginning or mid of the month.

In [ ]:

Recommendation¶

  1. More movies are needed, as the number of movies has declined since 2018, while the number of television shows has increased.
  2. Consider the popular actors and directors for that country when creating content, as well as the actor-director combination which is highly recommended.
  3. It is recommended to watch TV shows in Japan and South Korea. The anime genre is popular in Japan, while the drama genre is popular in South Korea.
  4. The content of international movies is recommended for indians with TV-14 rating.
  5. Netflix should be focusing on adding more movies in emerging countries like India, United Kingdom, Canada and France for Adult audience.
  6. It is recommended that comedies and dramas have more adults content for the USA audience.
  7. Preferred Duration of movies will be from 80-120 minutes.
